java.lang.Object

Type Parameters:
S - the type of node to be built

Direct Known Subclasses:
TextBuilder
public abstract class ShapeBuilder<S extends javafx.scene.shape.Shape, B extends ShapeBuilder<S,B>> extends NodeBuilder<S,B>
An abstract base class for building nodes, providing a fluent API for configuring and creating instances of the node type specified by the generic parameter N.
